<% layout("../layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="container my-5">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
      <h1 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h5 class="card-title">1. Introduction</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            Welcome to Homify. We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
          </p>

          <h5 class="card-title mt-4">2. Information We Collect</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            We collect information you provide directly to us, such as:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Email address and username</li>
            <li>Contact information</li>
            <li>Listing details and images</li>
            <li>Review and rating information</li>
          </ul>

          <h5 class="card-title mt-4">3. How We Use Your Information</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            Your information is used to:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
            <li>Process transactions and send confirmations</li>
            <li>Send service-related announcements</li>
            <li>Respond to inquiries and support requests</li>
          </ul>

          <h5 class="card-title mt-4">4. Data Security</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information. All passwords are encrypted and sensitive data is transmitted securely.
          </p>

          <h5 class="card-title mt-4">5. Third-Party Services</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            We use Cloudinary for image storage and MongoDB for database management. These services have their own privacy policies.
          </p>

          <h5 class="card-title mt-4">6. Contact Us</h5>
          <p class="card-text">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at support@homify.com.
          </p>

          <div class="alert alert-info mt-4" role="alert">
            <strong>Last Updated:</strong> March 2026
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary mt-4">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
